Hi guys!<br><br>I was just wondering what is the probability of an official Nintendo Switch port?<br><br>I heard there are unofficial homebrew ports which indicate it is possible but the trouble is as far as I know, once you ever sign the NDA and become an official Nintendo Developer at any point in your life, Nintendo can actually sue you for touching homebrew staff. It is actually included in their NDA once you sign it, you are not allowed to get involved with the homebrew community in any capacity.<br><br>So do you guys think there would ever be an official Nintendo Switch port available?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=177312">ddabrahim</a> — Sat Dec 30, 2023 6:15 pm</p><hr />
